{"tid":625830,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"依個休班警高質！","createTime":"2018-04-11T18:48:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-15T19:48:15.000Z","uid":579,"like":5,"dislike":31,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"6a0a7765c06bbfe4fc4cdb7fef211956853d2b26","tid":625830,"uid":579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T18:48:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180411/mobile/bkn-20180411132327424-0411_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180411%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20180411132327424-0411_00822_001.html&d=%2BLXYLlvNe20dysAnQriBOtU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=3f11995d\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180411/mobile/bkn-20180411132327424-0411_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/12/024611_3819ed163d9eac3226f2b158b612f44a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F12%2F024611_3819ed163d9eac3226f2b158b612f44a.png&h=3774e24b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n南亞劫案：街坊直斥離晒譜　香港人養佢哋仲搶錢<br />\n04月11日(三) 13:23   ONCC <br />\n <br />\n元朗南亞匪搶劫狂毆事主，由於案發在鬧市人來人往，有街坊直斥匪徒「離晒譜」。據目擊經過的陳伯稱，案發時，事主從滙豐銀行步出，即被2名匪徒截住，其中一人將事主按住，另一人則欲搶去其背包，惟事主反抗，於是2賊即揮拳向事主頭部「狂揼」，有途人見狀立即上前制止。2南亞匪見事敗，即沿康樂路往教育路方向逃走，其中身材高大的匪徒逃去無蹤，惟「矮啲嘅」逃跑約50米後，即被2名休班警合力制服。 <br />\n<br />\n是次劫案在光天化日下發生，陳伯直斥治安敗壞：「日光日白呢到咁多人都搶你嘢，你話香港治安點樣呢！」而不少南亞裔人士因酷刑聲請而留港，陳伯直指：「香港人養佢哋仲要搶嘢，係咪離譜啲呀。」他又稱，因年紀較大，若不幸遇劫會無力反抗，「梗係擔心啦，年紀咁大無力反抗㗎，惟有逃命咋！」故他表示日後外出會小心為上，盡量在大路行走，以確保安全。 <br />\n<br />\n而在附近回收二手物品的何先生，在場目擊劫案發生，「當時嗰個男人準備行入去存錢，突然見到佢好似跌親，之後就畀人拖咗出行人路」。何表示曾上前喝止，惟匪徒只是「望一望」，其後再次毆打男子。"},{"pid":"29d9cd0116aa74102aa38e0c7bf4744e4b67764a","tid":625830,"uid":64131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T18:57:24.000Z","msg":"網上行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49497ddc495df62d894d4cd64017d422fdfa1577","tid":625830,"uid":64131,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T19:02:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180411/mobile/bkn-20180411173841680-0411_00822_001.html?eventPath=hk_news&amp;eventID=402882b1624f38f80162b327bd590c34\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180411%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20180411173841680-0411_00822_001.html%3FeventPath%3Dhk_news%26eventID%3D402882b1624f38f80162b327bd590c34&d=%2BLXYLlvNe20dysAnQriBOtU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=bdcd8437\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180411/mobile/bkn-20180411173841680-0411_00822_001.html?eventPath=hk_news&amp;eventID=402882b1624f38f80162b327bd590c34</a><br />\n<br />\n屌你痴撚線<br />\n個街坊當住個休班警面前攞摺椅一野bang落個南亞人度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0cb8199f81787987c5950e965ec96a858a62333","tid":625830,"uid":579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"49497ddc495df62d894d4cd64017d422fdfa1577","tid":625830,"uid":64131,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T19:02:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180411/mobile/bkn-20180411173841680-0411_00822_001.html?eventPath=hk_news&amp;eventID=402882b1624f38f80162b327bd590c34\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180411%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20180411173841680-0411_00822_001.html%3FeventPath%3Dhk_news